Installation
------------
Make sure you have the latest version of pymongo installed (http://api.mongodb.org/python).

To install mango:

sudo python setup.py install

Usage
-----
To use mango with your Django project, just add these lines to your settings.py file:

SESSION_ENGINE = 'mango.session'
AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS = ('mango.auth.Backend',)

Also, make sure 'MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES' contains:

'django.contrib.sessions.middleware.SessionMiddleware'
'django.contrib.auth.middleware.AuthenticationMiddleware'
